spec_data.Name: gcc-c++-ppc64-linux-gnu
spec_data.License: GPLv3+ and GPLv3+ with exceptions and GPLv2+ with exceptions and LGPLv2+ and BSD
spec_data.Description:
Cross-build GNU C++ compiler.

Only the compiler is provided; not libstdc++.  Support for cross-building
user space programs is not currently provided as that would massively multiply
the number of packages.
